function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, false)-- disable spawned monster ai
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idActorSpawned, false)
end

unk_9c63f9d.value:
OWC_SMP_CHECK()
Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, SFX_WARN)

for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("SMP_Monsters")) do-- When player is within specified range, raise monsters using raise fx
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(actorID)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(actorID, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(actorID, true)
	
	Hydra.Wait(Hydra.GetRandomFloat(0, 0.2))-- wait to space out monster raise
end

unk_993f312.value:
ID_THIS_QUEST = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

bElite = Events.SMPShouldBeElite(idSelf)

Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, "spawner")

if bElite then
	SFX_WARN = SFX_WARN_MAJOR
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, "elite")
else
	SFX_WARN = SFX_WARN_MINOR
end
